
Version 0.4.1  08 Aug 2005
	Ability to toggle between all users / current user.

Version 0.4.0  30 May 2005
	Redesign for better GNOME HIG compatibility (based on ideas by Christian Storgaard).
	Added option for using theme default font.
	Minor improvements in RPM spec file (based on Pascal Bleser's <guru@unixtech.be> package).
	GTK >= 2.4.0 is required now.

Version 0.3.2  19 Apr 2005
	Added RPM spec file.

Version 0.3.1  17 Jun 2004
	Remove unneeded mingw dependancy for win32.

Version 0.3.0  12 Jun 2004
	GTK 2.4 compatibility

